Images:
- Adding a logo to a website
- Including photographs in a blog post
- Creating a button with an image background

Image Maps:
- Creating a clickable map of a country, with different regions linking to different pages
- Adding interactive hotspots to an image, where clicking on different areas leads to different content
- Creating a navigation bar with clickable images, where each image leads to a different page

Color:
- Setting the background color of a webpage
- Changing the color of text or links
- Adding color to borders or backgrounds of elements on a page.
